title: Hard to Handle
description:
Small time con artist Lefty Merrill has co-organized a crooked dance marathon and set-up his girlfriend to win the prize money. When his partner disappears with money before the contest is over, he&#039;s forced to come up with a series of cons to help pay it back.

Claire Dodd ...  Marlene Reeves 
Robert McWade ...  Charles G. Reeves
